Package ca.phon.phonexg4

Interface PhonexListener

All Superinterfaces:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
All Known Implementing Classes:
PhonexBaseListener, PhonexCompiler2
public interface PhonexListener extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by PhonexParser.
